2. Booking Management:
  - Implement a booking system that allows users to check availability, make reservations, and receive confirmation emails
  - Integrate payment gateway for secure online transactions

- Once users decide on a destination they would like to travel to and have explored relevant options they can book
- Booking options can include: flights, accommodation, transport, attractions, tours etc
- Booking functionality will allow users to book around specific dates and personal requirements
- Booking functionality will automatically filter and sort based on user searches for all available and relevant packages
- Booking functionality will provide a process for payments to allow users to pay all fees upfront and pay deposits if necessary
- Once booked and payed users will be able to enter their contact details to receive further information about their holiday
- Booking functionality will issue users with all details such as flight tickets, accommodation info, travel pick up etc